ASoC: Use SGTL5000_LINREG_VDDD_MASK instead of hardcoded mask value

We have defined SGTL5000_LINREG_VDDD_MASK in sgtl5000.h,
use it instead of hardcoded (0x1 << 4) - 1 for the mask.

